            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pasta is cooking, peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> chicken breast strips</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
